snippet.title: Kitty Kart 64 Trailer
snippet.description:
The light's green and it's time to race! Aim for the checkered flag and don't slow down! Get your adrenaline pumping, only 1,2,3 laps and you win! Easy to pick up, yet impossible to put down! Do you have what it takes to get first place?

Made for the 2023 lsdjam
